title: Torrey Meister at Home | Chapter 2
description: In November of 2013 Torrey won the Coldwater Classic Invitational and took home the "winner take all" grand prize, which was a sponsorship from O'Neill consisting of $50,000 to travel the world and compete in the World Qualifying Series in pursuit of making the World Championship Tour. This is Chapter 2 of his quest, surfing at home during the Hawaiian leg of the tour.
